cardinality: 1:1
required: true
```

### Relationship: Replay → Blueprints

```yaml
relationship: Replay → Blueprints
verb: exercises
cardinality: 1:many
required: true
```

### Relationship: Replay → Telemetry

```yaml
relationship: Replay → Telemetry
verb: feeds
cardinality: 1:1
required: true
```

### Relationship: UGVAdapter → Harness

```yaml
relationship: UGVAdapter → Harness
